        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#高速驾驶途中突然身体不舒服了怎么办#】#不要带着身体隐患长途高速驾驶# 春节假期，不少人都奔波在回家、返程、外出旅行的路上。交警提醒，长途出行前...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E9%80%94%E4%B8%AD%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E4%BA%86%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E9%80%94%E4%B8%AD%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E4%BA%86%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#高速驾驶途中突然身体不舒服了怎么办#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%B8%A6%E7%9D%80%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E9%9A%90%E6%82%A3%E9%95%BF%E9%80%94%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%B8%A6%E7%9D%80%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E9%9A%90%E6%82%A3%E9%95%BF%E9%80%94%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不要带着身体隐患长途高速驾驶#</span></a> 春节假期，不少人都奔波在回家、返程、外出旅行的路上。交警提醒，长途出行前一定要做足准备，尤其要关注自身身体情况，不要带着隐患开车，如果遇到突发情况，要第一时间报警求助。交警提醒，长途行驶精神长时间高度集中，体力消耗很大，稍感身体不适都可能会影响驾驶安全，因此长途驾驶前，驾驶人一定要关注自己的身体状况，并保证充足的休息，以确保行驶安全。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4862253200244874" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网快看的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/75dda851ly8hahb6fwxuoj21hc0u0ajd.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/iAYwdRB6lx082ETAMuSk01041200XJ1Y0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674883218&amp;ssig=k6Ls1j5qKs&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/ngF3rWtAlx082ETAyFfi01041200wKt60E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674883218&amp;ssig=bNSIZPWYuk&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/QdZ5mFfllx082ETzkfwI01041200jTaV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1674883218&amp;ssig=gsY9y3%2F4Bz&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4862253200244874&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
